{"tid":1517844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王丹: 831大遊行將是關鍵時刻, 希望港人都站出來","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:30:23.000Z","uid":265179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69b7882db8e978246bd1d81d60313588edf41939","tid":1517844,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:56:18.000Z","msg":"王丹网站 Wang Dan's Page<br />\n3 hrs &middot; <br />\n岑子杰被襲擊，黃之鋒被捕，陳浩天被拒絕離境。大逮捕就要開始了。中共顯然是要抓捕大部分有號召力的抗爭組織者。<br />\n鎮壓的時刻就要到了。港人退無可退。必須保護黃之鋒這些人，否則，下一個被捕的人就是你。<br />\n831大遊行，當局會評估港人面對進一步鎮壓的抗壓度。那將是關鍵時刻。希望港人都站出來。<br />\n也再次呼籲台灣的民間團體或者政黨，能夠發動大遊行，聲援和救救香港！<br />\n(from王丹fb)"},{"pid":"4185129fe7384f4010ac9924e9e4a09bbb0787d0","tid":1517844,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />敵人反對我擁護"},{"pid":"438e6d6a0939e44e2bae2b6cb3c4f6e972ef908a","tid":1517844,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4185129fe7384f4010ac9924e9e4a09bbb0787d0","tid":1517844,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />敵人反對我擁護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"香港人唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e9d04996bbbbae12b64ce7158675053295a304","tid":1517844,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"}]}